        Constructor Loan. This method creates a new loan. There should be at least one money lender.
        Parameters:
        n - contains the name of the new loan. String, cann't be empty neither null.
        a - contains the amount of the of the loan. Long, cann't be null.
        cD - contains the creation date of the loan. Calendar, cann't be null, neither a future date.
        pD - contains the pay date of this loan. Calendar, cann't be null.
        ml - contains the money lender who lends this money.
